                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6381" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0311</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8274 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西立讯智造：“后疫情”情况下组织结构变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jiangxi   Luxshare  Intelligent  Manufacture : The road to organizational structure change in the &quot;post- Covid-19 pandemic &quot; situation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏海涛，殷芙蓉，杨学新，王丽，刘德华</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南昌大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张和平</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西立讯智造有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西立讯智造；危机事件；矩阵式组织结构；组织结构变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jiangxi   Luxshare  Intelligent  Manufacture；Crisis Event; Matrix Organisation Structure; Organisational Change</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">面对突入其来的新冠疫情，处在制造业的江西立讯智造全面应战，但后疫情时代给江西立讯智造带来了公司人员复工难、人员减少以及订单回流人手急剧不足等危机，同时疫情后暴露了之前就存在的部分问题。公司为了满足自身发展战略，积极调整了部门组织结构，以公司内部的声学&amp;EE工程处为试点部门，为保证团队绩效，将组织结构调整为矩阵式组织结构，提升了团队工作效率，帮助企业度过危机。本案例旨在通过情景让学生了解组织结构在公司运营中的重要性，结合组织结构的相关知识点，积极思考当组织面临危机事件时该如何在组织结构方面应对，同时作为面对突发危机事件的一个启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the face of the sudden arrival of the Covid-19 Pandemic, Jiangxi Luxshare responded comprehensively, but the post-epidemic era brought a crisis to Jiangxi Luxshare in which the  personnel had difficulty returning to work, reduced staff and a sharp shortage of manpower for order return, while the epidemic exposed some of the problems that existed before. To meet its own development strategy, the company actively adjusted its human resource allocation and used the acoustics department within the company as a pilot department.To ensure team performance, the organizational structure was adjusted to a matrix organizational structure, which improved teamwork efficiency and helped the company survive the crisis. This case aims to let students understand the importance of organizational structure in company operations through scenarios, and to actively consider how to respond in terms of organizational structure when the organization faces a crisis event in conjunction with the relevant knowledge points of organizational structure, as well as to serve as a revelation in the face of unexpected crisis events.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">掌握内外部环境分析；了解机械式组织结构与有机式组织结构、影响组织变化的因素；认识矩阵式组织结构以及矩阵式组织结构的优点</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
